query:
SELECT convenio, COUNT(*) as qtd FROM (
  SELECT operadora_1 as convenio FROM pacientes WHERE operadora_1 IS NOT NULL AND operadora_1 != ''
  UNION ALL
  SELECT operadora_2 FROM pacientes WHERE operadora_2 IS NOT NULL AND operadora_2 != ''
) t
GROUP BY convenio
ORDER BY qtd DESC;
